 class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 04, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104hor1665703135893.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hor1665703135893.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hor1665703135893.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"hor1665703135893\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"hor1665703135893__upsetocc_408326\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Make the specified occurrence current.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"hor1665703135893__topic_d123530e1_d123531e1_d123532e1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104hor1665703135893_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"hor1665703135893__codeblock_e4b_5ck_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">long upsetocc (unsigned char*entity, longoccnum);</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hor1665703135893__topic_d87297e1_d87298e1_d87299e1_d87300e1_d87301e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1007761e61\">Parameters</h2>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"hor1665703135893__parml_mfn_vck_bwb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">entity</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Name of the entity. You can specify zero or an empty string to denote the current\n                  entity.</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">occnum</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Sequence number of the occurrence that must be made current. Specify -1 to make\n                  the last occurrence current.</dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hor1665703135893__topic_d87302e1_d87303e1_d87304e1_d87305e1_d87306e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1007761e90\">Return Values</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"hor1665703135893__table_d14984e1_d14985e1_d14986e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned by upsetocc</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"hor1665703135893__table_d14984e1_d14985e1_d14986e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"hor1665703135893__table_d14984e1_d14985e1_d14986e1__entry__2\">Meaning</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hor1665703135893__table_d14984e1_d14985e1_d14986e1__entry__1\">&gt;0</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hor1665703135893__table_d14984e1_d14985e1_d14986e1__entry__2\">The sequence number of the new current\n                        occurrence</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hor1665703135893__table_d14984e1_d14985e1_d14986e1__entry__1\">-1</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hor1665703135893__table_d14984e1_d14985e1_d14986e1__entry__2\">The occurrence could not be made current. Most\n                        likely causes: <var class=\"keyword varname\">Occnum</var> is out of range, or\n                           <var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var> does not exist, or it is not painted on the\n                        component.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hor1665703135893__topic_d87307e1_d87308e1_d87309e1_d87310e1_d87311e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1007761e148\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hor1665703135893__d5947e20\">Library:  <span class=\"ph filepath\">yrtl</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hor1665703135893__topic_d87312e1_d87313e1_d87314e1_d87315e1_d87316e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1007761e161\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hor1665703135893__p_d123557e1_d123558e1_d123559e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">upsetocc</code> makes the occurrence of\n               <var class=\"keyword varname\">entity</var> with sequence number <var class=\"keyword varname\">occnum</var> the current\n            occurrence.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hor1665703135893__p_d123560e1_d123561e1_d123562e1\">The argument <var class=\"keyword varname\">entity</var> is the name of the entity whose occurrence will be made current. If <var class=\"keyword varname\">entity</var> is zero or is an empty string, the current entity is used. You can specify -1 for <var class=\"keyword varname\">occnum</var> to make the last occurrence current.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hor1665703135893__p_d123563e1_d123564e1_d123565e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">upsetocc</code> is equivalent to the\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">setocc</span> ProcScript statement.</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104hor1665703135893_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"hor1665703135893__codeblock_fbq_fdk_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">#include &lt;h3gl.h&gt;\nEXPORT void set_last_occ ()\n{\n(void) upsetocc(\"\", -1); /* Make the last occurrence current */\n}</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ryi1665703135669.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>upaddocc</a><p>Create an empty occurrence of an entity.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/crd1665703135753.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>updelocc</a><p>Remove an occurrence of the specified entity from the hitlist.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qem1665703135824.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>updisocc</a><p>Discard one or more occurrences of the specified entity from the hitlist.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528311\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528311\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "upsetocc Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 04, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Make the specified occurrence current. Explain this code long upsetocc (unsigned char*entity, longoccnum); Copy Parameters entity Name of the entity. You can specify zero or an empty string to denote the current entity. occnum Sequence number of the occurrence that must be made current. Specify -1 to make the last occurrence current. Return Values Table 1. Values returned by upsetocc Value Meaning >0 The sequence number of the new current occurrence -1 The occurrence could not be made current. Most likely causes: Occnum is out of range, or Entity does not exist, or it is not painted on the component. Use Library: yrtl Description upsetocc makes the occurrence of entity with sequence number occnum the current occurrence. The argument entity is the name of the entity whose occurrence will be made current. If entity is zero or is an empty string, the current entity is used. You can specify -1 for occnum to make the last occurrence current. upsetocc is equivalent to the setocc ProcScript statement. Explain this code #include <h3gl.h> EXPORT void set_last_occ () { (void) upsetocc(\"\", -1); /* Make the last occurrence current */ } Copy Related Links upaddocc Create an empty occurrence of an entity. updelocc Remove an occurrence of the specified entity from the hitlist. updisocc Discard one or more occurrences of the specified entity from the hitlist. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}